<chapter condition="TITLE=System Features - Schedule Report;PERM=sy_cust_report_schedule;ACCESS=SY_BTC_RD"
         role="TOPIC">
  <title>Schedule Report Module</title>

  <para role="TEXT">As an administrator at a bank, you use the Schedule Report
  module to schedule reports to be executed automatically at a given
  frequency, with the results sent to a specified recipient via email. There
  is no need for any user to actually be connected to <xi:include
  href="../entities_en.xml" xpointer="ent_appli"
  xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"/> while a scheduled report is
  running. The report is executed as if it was being run by a user with access
  to the bank's full jurisdiction (that is, with access to all available
  permissions given to the bank and all its entities). You can select the
  format (<type>CSV</type>, <type>Spreadsheet</type> or <type>PDF</type>) of
  the results sent as an email attachment and the language in which the report
  is generated.</para>

  <para>You cannot customise the actual time of day when a scheduled report is
  executed. This is configured in the technical properties of the MP
  application and defined by the Bank technical administrator.</para>

  <section role="ITEM" condition="TITLE=System Features - Schedule Report;PERM=sy_cust_report_schedule;ACCESS=SY_BTC_RD" >
    <title>Schedule Function</title>

    <para>This module consists of one function called <emphasis
    role="bold">Schedule</emphasis>, which is in the <emphasis
    role="bold">Report Designer</emphasis> part of the System Features
    menu.</para>

    <para>When you click this function, you are presented with a list of all
    the existing scheduled reports. You can search the list by entering search
    criteria in the <guilabel moreinfo="none">Report Name</guilabel> and/or
    <guilabel moreinfo="none">Frequency</guilabel> fields at the top of the
    page.</para>

    <para>The list of scheduled reports has the following columns:</para>

    <informaltable role="TEXT">
      <tgroup cols="2">
        <colspec colname="c1" colwidth="2.0*"/>

        <colspec colname="c2" colwidth="8.0*"/>

        <thead>
          <row>
            <entry valign="top"><para>Field</para></entry>

            <entry valign="top"><para>Description</para></entry>
          </row>
        </thead>

        <tbody>
          <row>
            <entry valign="top"><para><guilabel moreinfo="none">Report
            Name</guilabel> </para></entry>

            <entry valign="top"><para>Report Name</para></entry>
          </row>

          <row>
            <entry valign="top"><para><guilabel
            moreinfo="none">Frequency</guilabel> </para></entry>

            <entry valign="top"><para>Batch Frequency (<type>Daily</type>,
            <type>Weekly</type> or <type>Monthly</type>). Depending on the
            frequency, additional information is provided:</para><itemizedlist>
                <listitem>
                  <para><type>Weekly</type>: the abbreviated name for the
                  chosen day of the week.</para>
                </listitem>

                <listitem>
                  <para><type>Monthly</type>: the day of the month (as a
                  number).</para>
                </listitem>
              </itemizedlist></entry>
          </row>

          <row>
            <entry valign="top"><para><guilabel moreinfo="none">Output
            Format</guilabel> </para></entry>

            <entry valign="top"><para>Chosen Output format
            :</para><itemizedlist>
                <listitem>
                  <para><type>CSV</type>: Comma Separated Value.</para>
                </listitem>

                <listitem>
                  <para><type>Spreadsheet</type>: format compatible with
                  <productname class="trade">Microsoft
                  Excel</productname>.</para>
                </listitem>

                <listitem>
                  <para><type>PDF</type>: <productname class="trade">Adobe
                  Acrobat</productname> format.</para>
                </listitem>
              </itemizedlist></entry>
          </row>

          <row>
            <entry valign="top"><para><guilabel moreinfo="none">Next
            Batch</guilabel> </para></entry>

            <entry valign="top"><para>For information, the date of the next
            report execution is indicated.</para></entry>
          </row>
        </tbody>
      </tgroup>
    </informaltable>

    <para role="TEXT">You can modify an entry by clicking the <guiicon
    moreinfo="none">Edit</guiicon> <inlinemediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="../images/icon_edit.gif" role="ICON_EDIT"
                     width="4mm"/>
        </imageobject>
      </inlinemediaobject> icon in the right-hand column, or delete it by
    clicking the <guibutton moreinfo="none">Delete</guibutton>
    <inlinemediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="../images/icon_trash.gif" role="ICON_TRASH"
                     width="4mm"/>
        </imageobject>
      </inlinemediaobject> icon.</para>

    <para role="TEXT">Click the <guibutton moreinfo="none">Add</guibutton>
    button at the bottom of the list to add an report to the schedule.</para>

    <section role="ITEM">
      <title>Schedule Report Form</title>

      <para role="TEXT"><guiicon moreinfo="none">Edit</guiicon> and <guibutton
      moreinfo="none">Add</guibutton> display the same form, but in the case
      of <guibutton moreinfo="none">Add</guibutton> it is blank and in the
      case of <guibutton moreinfo="none">Edit</guibutton> it is preset with
      the existing details of the schedule for the report. After entering the
      details, click <emphasis role="bold">Save</emphasis> at the bottom of
      the form.</para>

      <para>The form is as follows:</para>

      <para><informaltable role="TEXT">
          <tgroup cols="3">
            <colspec colname="c1" colwidth="3.0*"/>

            <colspec colname="c2" colwidth="1.0*"/>

            <colspec colname="c3" colwidth="5.0*"/>

            <thead>
              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para>Field</para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para>Type</para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para>Description</para></entry>
              </row>
            </thead>

            <tbody>
              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para><guilabel moreinfo="none">Report
                Name</guilabel></para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para> <inlinemediaobject>
                    <imageobject>
                      <imagedata fileref="../images/char_arrow.gif"
                                 role="CHAR_ARROW" width="2mm"/>
                    </imageobject>
                  </inlinemediaobject><inlinemediaobject>
                    <imageobject>
                      <imagedata fileref="../images/char_excla.gif"
                                 role="CHAR_EXCLA" width="2mm"/>
                    </imageobject>
                  </inlinemediaobject> </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para>Selection of the
                report</para></entry>
              </row>

              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para><guilabel
                moreinfo="none">Frequency</guilabel> </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para> <inlinemediaobject>
                    <imageobject>
                      <imagedata fileref="../images/char_radio.gif"
                                 role="CHAR_RADIO" width="2mm"/>
                    </imageobject>
                  </inlinemediaobject><inlinemediaobject>
                    <imageobject>
                      <imagedata fileref="../images/char_excla.gif"
                                 role="CHAR_EXCLA" width="2mm"/>
                    </imageobject>
                  </inlinemediaobject> </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para>Three choices are
                available:</para><itemizedlist>
                    <listitem>
                      <para><type>Daily</type></para>
                    </listitem>

                    <listitem>
                      <para><type>Weekly</type>: the user has to choose the
                      day of the week.</para>
                    </listitem>

                    <listitem>
                      <para><type>Monthly</type>: the user has to select the
                      day of the month</para>
                    </listitem>
                  </itemizedlist></entry>
              </row>

              <row>
                <entry><guilabel>Output Format</guilabel></entry>

                <entry><inlinemediaobject>
                    <imageobject>
                      <imagedata fileref="../images/char_arrow.gif"
                                 role="CHAR_ARROW" width="2mm"/>
                    </imageobject>
                  </inlinemediaobject> <inlinemediaobject>
                    <imageobject>
                      <imagedata fileref="../images/char_excla.gif"
                                 role="CHAR_EXCLA" width="2mm"/>
                    </imageobject>
                  </inlinemediaobject></entry>

                <entry><para>The format of the attachment containing the
                results of the report and which is going to be included in the
                email sent upon the scheduled date is defined
                here:</para><itemizedlist>
                    <listitem>
                      <para><type>CSV</type> for a Comma Separated Value
                      file,</para>
                    </listitem>

                    <listitem>
                      <para><type>Spreadsheet</type> for a format compatible
                      with <productname class="trade">Microsoft
                      Excel</productname>,</para>
                    </listitem>

                    <listitem>
                      <para><type>PDF</type> <productname class="trade">for
                      the Adobe Acrobat</productname> format.</para>
                    </listitem>
                  </itemizedlist></entry>
              </row>

              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para><guilabel moreinfo="none">Language /
                Locale</guilabel> </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para> <inlinemediaobject>
                    <imageobject>
                      <imagedata fileref="../images/char_arrow.gif"
                                 role="CHAR_ARROW" width="2mm"/>
                    </imageobject>
                  </inlinemediaobject> <inlinemediaobject>
                    <imageobject>
                      <imagedata fileref="../images/char_excla.gif"
                                 role="CHAR_EXCLA" width="2mm"/>
                    </imageobject>
                  </inlinemediaobject> </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para>Select box with all available
                languages. This choice will determine in which language the
                report will be executed and therefore the language of the
                results. It is also used to set the language of the actual
                email message.</para></entry>
              </row>

              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para><guilabel moreinfo="none">Email
                Address</guilabel> </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para> <inlinemediaobject>
                    <imageobject>
                      <imagedata fileref="../images/char_excla.gif"
                                 role="CHAR_EXCLA" width="2mm"/>
                    </imageobject>
                  </inlinemediaobject> </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para>The email address of the recipient
                (40 characters maximum). </para></entry>
              </row>
            </tbody>
          </tgroup>
        </informaltable></para>
    </section>
  </section>
</chapter>
